<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

With the '''Std ProjectUtil''' command you can extract files from a FreeCAD document ({{FileName|*.FCStd}}), which is in fact a [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zip_(file_format) ZIP] file, and, after manual edits, create a new document from them.

[[Image:Project_utility_en.png]]
{{Caption|The Project Utility dialog box}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Применение==

===Extract Document===

# Select the {{MenuCommand|Tools → [[Image:Std_ProjectUtil.svg|16px]] Document Utility}} option from the menu.
# The '''Project Utility''' dialog box opens.
# Press the {{Button|…}} button to the right of {{MenuCommand|Extract Document → Source}}.
# Select the {{FileName|*.FCStd}} file you want to edit.
# Press the {{Button|…}} button to the right of {{MenuCommand|Extract Document → Destination}}.
# Select a folder where the document should be extracted. It is advisable to select an empty folder.
# Press the {{Button|Extract}} button.
# Press the {{Button|Close}} button to close the dialog box.

===Manual edits===

It is important to realize that the files inside a FreeCAD document are interlinked. Only editing a single file will typically lead to errors. To make consistent edits across multiple files use a good code editor, such as [https://notepad-plus-plus.org/ Notepad++] (for Windows) or [https://notepadqq.com/s/ Notepadqq] (for Linux).

<span id="Create_Document"></span>
===Создание проекта===

# Select the {{MenuCommand|Tools → [[Image:Std_ProjectUtil.svg|16px]] Project Utility}} option from the menu.
# The '''Project utility''' dialog box opens.
# Press the {{Button|…}} button to the right of {{MenuCommand|Create Document → Source}}.
# Select the {{FileName|Document.xml}} file. The command will be automatically find all linked files.
# Press the {{Button|…}} button to the right of {{MenuCommand|Create Document → Destination}}.
# Select a folder where the new document should be created.
# Press the {{Button|Create}} button.
# A new document with a fixed name, {{FileName|project.fcstd}}, is created in the selected folder. There is no warning if a file with that name already exists.
# Optionally check the '''Load document after creation''' checkbox.
# Press the {{Button|Close}} button to close the dialog box.

<span id="Notes"></span>
==Примечания==

* For more information about the FreeCAD document file format see [[File_Format_FCStd|File Format FCStd]].


